sources.title: As Dreamers Do: The Amazing Life of Walt Disney | 2014
sources.description:
**This film is under license from Vision Films Inc.  All rights reserved**

As Dreamers Do: The Amazing Life of Walt Disney - Behind every great mouse there is a man - Armed with an ever growing imagination and eternal optimism, Walt begins to develop skills as an animator early in life. He overcomes a variety of hardships to become one of the biggest icons in the world: Walt Disney.  Stars Travis Tritt, Olan Rogers, Ryan Dunlap
